<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard Redirect Test Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: #334155;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #8b5cf6;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #2563eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>🎉 Redirect Successful!</h1>
        <p>You have successfully been redirected to the secondary test page by the Admin Dashboard.</p>
        <p>The tracker script is still running here, so the Admin can continue to monitor or redirect you again.</p>
        <a href="/">Return to Main Index</a>
    </div>

    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="js/tracker.js"></script>
</body>

</html>